<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.FilterPluginsOfFamilyBelowVersion" Title="FilterPluginsOfFamilyBelowVersion method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator">RenderPluginEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    FilterPluginsOfFamilyBelowVersion
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterPluginsOfFamilyBelowVersion</TypeRef> method removes renderer plugins of the specified API family whose target version is below the supplied version.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterPluginsOfFamilyBelowVersion(IRendererPlugin::ApiFamily apiFamily, IRendererPlugin::ApiVersion apiVersion);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="ApiFamily!cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.ApiFamily" Name="apiFamily">
          The API family to test.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="ApiVersion!cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.ApiVersion" Name="apiVersion">
          The minimum version to keep for that family.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
